{"tid":1646522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議撰寫抗爭日程規則","createTime":"2019-10-11T10:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T09:45:48.000Z","uid":312692,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"95af0b7655b482d8a4b940bb96f2913caa9e6ea4","tid":1646522,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"早前活動好有效而且集中<br />\n香港之路、交通壓力測試...係有目共睹<br />\n雖然部分原因係班狗仲㩒得住<br />\n<br />\n但10.1啲狗發癲之後<br />\n除咗有共識既各區開花外<br />\n活動文宣一個接一個<br />\n有啲仲要係冇原因突然出現<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n我建議撰寫抗爭日程規則<br />\n例如 : <br />\n-規定活動必需係前幾日開post<br />\n-長期置頂集中抗爭日程post<br />\n-快閃活動另外開post，不可納入抗爭日程表<br />\n-設立活動及風險分級制<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 1級~緊急活動(當日有重大議題公佈)</span><br />\n <span style=\"color: purple;\">2級~次緊急活動(遊行，開花，裝修，和你塞)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"> 3級~一般活動(人鏈，商場唱歌，街坊集會)</span><br />\n <span style=\"color: green;\">N級~日常活動(懲罰黃店，每日口罩)</span><br />\n-優先推<span style=\"color: red;\">緊急活動</span><br />\n<br />\n有冇更加好既建議？"},{"pid":"0c31bc61d670f56051b5d40c47aa5fdda6c9adac","tid":1646522,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:32:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68e2e316cc4a4d9a4c8bd092dabf742237bfb27c","tid":1646522,"uid":82253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:32:17.000Z","msg":"率先參與自我分類<br />\n<br />\n籃球活動：1025-26#StandWithMorey榮光盃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646298</a><br />\n<br />\n3級 非緊急"},{"pid":"7c1c2f12aaad1a9ec970da0f9a918f7cc83286c6","tid":1646522,"uid":82253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68e2e316cc4a4d9a4c8bd092dabf742237bfb27c","tid":1646522,"uid":82253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:32:17.000Z","msg":"率先參與自我分類<br />\n<br />\n籃球活動：1025-26#StandWithMorey榮光盃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646298</a><br />\n<br />\n3級 非緊急"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1